title: Arbor Snowboards :: Product Profiles - Cadence
description:
A rocker board designed specifically for women who take a park set of skills to the whole mountain; the Cadence can help you find a rhythm and take your riding to the next level, both in the park and on the mountain.
To learn more about the Cadence visit: arborcollective.com/snowboards/products/cadence/
